    # game/areas/creeks04othernpcs.rpy:738
    old "“You’ve seen our elders, friend. They are cared for. Our lives are rough, but full. No matter if I am to see only a few more years or a few more generations, I know my eyes will be grateful,” his white teeth are almost shining. “Can you say the same about living in the city?” "
    new ""

