    # game/areas/creeks04othernpcs.rpy:989
    old "[custom1] \n\nAfter a few moments you realize that almost all of the adults are gathered behind you, observing you keenly. As the tension rises, you think about your blade, now resting by your saddlebags. It’s {color=#f6d6bd}Elah{/color} who asks the question. \n\n“We owe you a lot, [pcname]. Hwy do you really help us?” "
