    # game/areas/creeks04othernpcs.rpy:1000
    old "“{color=#f6d6bd}Old Hava{/color} was right,” says one of the farmers. “So {i}that’s{/i} hwy they sent the second one,” adds a woodcutter. The fuss stops as quickly as it started, cut by the loud voice of the drunk {color=#f6d6bd}Efren{/color}. “Let the roadwarden make a case for it!” \n\nYou glance at the eyes of the locals. Some of them are distrustful, others are curious, and a few are excited. Even though you already recognize many of these faces, the dancing flames make them look like a strange crowd awaiting a prophecy. "
